reviewText: okay... idk wth the other people that reviewed this are talking about, but this dvd is GARBAGE!! & i'll tell you why.. the model is very attractive & it is always beautiful to see beautiful women nude! but it's the insane crazy camera angles & shots the camera man shoots that just destroy what otherwise would have been a pretty awesome(besides it being relatively short in running time) hott nude massage dvd!! they seriously need to fire their camera guys & hire new ones! & its the same issue with the other nude massage dvd(produced by the same guy/company) i purchased: ''Nude Massage featuring Jayden and Ashlynn - a Nude-Art Film'', but that 1 is actually longer in showing time & the camera angles aren't as bad as this dvd is(although the camera man does shoot the same 'odd', 'weird' ass shots & angles which is very frustrating! which is what made me purchase this other 1 to see if it was just that 1 dvd). but this 1 takes the cake!! its shorter in length time & the camera man is soooo ridiculously horrible with his camera angles & shots!!!!! i honestly don't know wtf is on his or the editing peoples mind!! just horribleness man..horrible!! they have certain shots & scenes where the camera & whole scene shot is damn near still & focuses on an absolutely obsolete part of the models body(upper thigh or leg, or left foot..) its absolutely retarded & just doesnt make any real sense!! it completely screws up the entire dvd! not worth the purchase, idk wtf these dudes were thinking when it came to camera angles, shots & editing. they're crazy for putting this out like that, it's a crime & a very frustrating waste of $$
Nice attractive models however it would be better if both were nude and were more explicit with their bodies and camera shots.

Fantastic meaning "in the realm of fantasy' which is what this girl Sarah is. I should say I own the Blu-Ray of this. The girl is amazing. There is nothing naughty going on, just a beautiful, beautiful woman getting a massage. The camera goes everywhere you want it to go. I wish the photosets on the Davids Nudes discs were more 'flippable', more of a folder than a movie of photo sets. But I can't even take off a star for this because of the video material. The girl GIVING the massage is also real hot, fully clothed but some nice yoga pants action. This is why High Definition was invented.
